des:
Prosper Insights and Analytics now offers its comprehensive Consumer Behavior data and Consumer Confidence Information by Voice! Get a Daily Briefing of key insights into consumer preferences and trends, and ask for more specific data by industry or company. Industries include retail, automotive, media, finance, and much more. Get overall consumer sentiment in any area, just by asking.
